/*
  Wave order (prerequisites before activating this spec):

  Wave 1 — must be green:
    - rate-setter-sync.spec.ts        (RS-REG-01, 02, 06, 07)
    - auto-rename.spec.ts             (AR-REG-01 smoke)
  Otherwise share-link failures will be falsely attributed to
  share-link logic when they are actually regressions upstream.

  Wave 2 — this spec:
    - SL-REG-01, 02, 03 (happy path + scope).
    - SL-REG-08 (invalid input).

  Wave 3 — after share-link permission UI lands (DAD, TBD):
    - SL-REG-04, 05 (comment permission).
    - SL-REG-06, 07 (revocation).

  Fixtures required:
    - A persistent FIXTURE_PROJECT_SLUG project in staging Supabase,
      seeded with deterministic set of approved/rejected/draft photos.
    - Two test auth identities: qa-owner + a dummy "guest-hash" marker
      used by comments table.

  Selectors:
    - Use `data-test="..."` attributes exclusively, not classes or
      structural nth-child. Request DAD to add these in the share-link
      modal and share-gallery view.

  Backend dependencies:
    - `/api/signup` is NOT required for this spec (guest is anon).
    - `share_links` table + RLS policy + revocation flag must be live.

  Out of scope for this draft:
    - Token rotation / expiry (separate spec: share-link-rotation).
    - Signed approval events from guests (separate spec).
    - Analytics on share-link opens (separate spec, out of product scope
      for beta).
*/
